== 爭議 ==
一般華文傳媒用“假球案”稱呼此事實為極大謬誤。因為至今為止仍沒有發現於04-06年期間有任何操縱比賽结果（即所謂打假球）的情況出現，包括被罰降班的尤文圖斯有關的比賽。尤文圖斯受FIGC指控的是“違反公平競爭”的條例。

於2010年4月20日拿坡里刑事法庭上，莫吉的辯護律師團上交了3000條先前未曾暴光的錄音，其中更有現任國際米蘭主席莫拉堤及已故前主席范察堤與球證指派員貝爾加莫的錄音<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/86/italy/2010/04/13/1876928/calciopoli-watch-court-accepts-luciano-moggis-defence |title=Calciopoli Watch: Court Accepts Luciano Moggi's Defence Evidence Regarding Inter's Involvement In Explosive Day Of Calciopoli Hearings |access-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100610223316/http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/86/italy/2010/04/13/1876928/calciopoli-watch-court-accepts-luciano-moggis-defence |archive-date=2010-06-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同日拿坡里法庭亦接受了此批錄音作為呈堂證供<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/86/italy/2010/04/21/1889102/official-italian-fa-open-new-calciopoli-investigation |title=OFFICIAL: Italian FA Open New Calciopoli Investigation |access-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100426023241/http://www.goal.com/en-us/news/86/italy/2010/04/21/1889102/official-italian-fa-open-new-calciopoli-investigation |archive-date=2010-04-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。因此為何06年時與國際米蘭有關的錄音沒有被調查成為了一大爭議。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.football-italia.net/jul13dd.html |title=Fiorentina want Calciopoli explanation |accessdate=2011-07-23 |archive-date=2011-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110716203333/http://www.football-italia.net/jul13dd.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.163news.net/news/sports/28716.html |title=加总质疑电话门判决公正性为何有些窃听遭无视 |access-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120801131124/http://www.163news.net/news/sports/28716.html |archive-date=2012-08-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>甚至有認為將06年冠軍判給國際米蘭，<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/10/italy/2010/04/08/1869275/italian-fa-players-association-send-mixed-messages-over-new |title=Italian FA & Players Association Send Mixed Messages Over New Calciopoli |access-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100411222124/http://www.goal.com/en/news/10/italy/2010/04/08/1869275/italian-fa-players-association-send-mixed-messages-over-new |archive-date=2010-04-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 以及06年對尤文圖斯的處罰是錯誤。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/596/exclusive/2011/01/26/2324215/exclusive-juventus-were-wrongly-stripped-of-deserved-titles |title=Exclusive: Juventus Were Wrongly Stripped Of Deserved Titles By Calciopoli - Former Inter Coach |access-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110129160417/http://www.goal.com/en/news/596/exclusive/2011/01/26/2324215/exclusive-juventus-were-wrongly-stripped-of-deserved-titles |archive-date=2011-01-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/3276/serie-a/2010/10/09/2157912/calciopoli-watch-key-policeman-says-there-was-no-proof-to-punish- |title=Calciopoli Watch: Key policeman says there was no proof to punish Luciano Moggi & Juventus in 2006 trial |access-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101013084410/http://www.goal.com/en-gb/news/3276/serie-a/2010/10/09/2157912/calciopoli-watch-key-policeman-says-there-was-no-proof-to-punish- |archive-date=2010-10-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

同年尤文圖斯主席安德魯·阿涅尼決定向FIGC就06年的冠軍上訴，於2011年7月FIGC駁回上訴，維持06年意甲冠軍仍由國際米蘭擁有。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/10/italy/2011/07/18/2580357/figc-decides-inter-will-keep-2006-title-following-latest |title=FIGC decides Inter will keep 2006 title following latest Calciopoli investigations |access-date=2011-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722202324/http://www.goal.com/en/news/10/italy/2011/07/18/2580357/figc-decides-inter-will-keep-2006-title-following-latest |archive-date=2011-07-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>尤文圖斯決定上訴。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Juventus will appeal against FIGC's decision not to strip Inter of 2006 Scudetto - Goal.com|url=http://www.goal.com/en/news/10/italy/2011/07/18/2580700/juventus-will-appeal-against-figcs-decision-not-to-strip|access-date=2011-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110722144750/http://www.goal.com/en/news/10/italy/2011/07/18/2580700/juventus-will-appeal-against-figcs-decision-not-to-strip|archive-date=2011-07-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>

